\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {7}{\ignorespaces Clean Energy Foundation Model Deployment Framework (CEFMDF). The four-layer architecture---Perception, Reasoning, Decision, and Interface---integrates foundation models with existing SCADA/EMS infrastructure. Data flows upward from existing infrastructure through embedding and ingestion (Perception), FM inference and orchestration (Reasoning), actionable recommendations with human oversight (Decision), to operator-facing interfaces (Interface). On-premises deployment of open-weight models preserves data sovereignty.}}{21}{figure.7}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:cefmdf}{{7}{21}{Clean Energy Foundation Model Deployment Framework (CEFMDF). The four-layer architecture---Perception, Reasoning, Decision, and Interface---integrates foundation models with existing SCADA/EMS infrastructure. Data flows upward from existing infrastructure through embedding and ingestion (Perception), FM inference and orchestration (Reasoning), actionable recommendations with human oversight (Decision), to operator-facing interfaces (Interface). On-premises deployment of open-weight models preserves data sovereignty}{figure.7}{}}
